name: TRIP REPORT | Delta Air Lines Airbus A330-300 (COMFORT+) Atlanta to Minneapolis
description:
The latest installment in my series of trip reports on Delta Air Lines, but on a heavy for once! N803NW, a former Northwest Airlines Airbus A330-300, took me on what may have been the most relaxing flight of this series in Delta Comfort+, the US carrier's Economy Plus offering. Fun fact - I wasn't actually supposed to be on this flight. Thanks to the 2 hour delay on my Huntsville to Atlanta leg, I ended up missing what would have been my first 757 flight and was rebooked on this A330 instead. Not a bad consolation prize! I hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
